March 10 (Reuters) - Tesla Inc (TSLA.O) Chief Executive Officer Elon Musk has exercised options to acquire 10,500 shares of the electric-vehicle maker, U.S. securities filing showed on Friday. (This story has been corrected to say that Musk has exercised option to buy Tesla shares and removes reference to $50,000 in headline and paragraph 1) Our Standards: The Thomson Reuters Trust Principles.